Clover-for-Grails plugin integrates Atlassian Clover with the Grails framework. 
Project is open-source, based on the Apache License version 2.0. 

Documentation: http://confluence.atlassian.com/display/CLOVER/Clover+Documentation+Home

Issue tracker: http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/CLOV (report under the "Grails Plugin" component)

Technical support: http://support.atlassian.com

Download page: http://grails.org/plugin/clover

Clover home page: http://www.atlassian.com/clover 
